Text: I joined the Problem Solvers Caucus because I, like most Americans, believe partisan politics are preventing Congress from addressing our nation's most pressing issues. I'm proud of the work our Caucus is doing to promote bipartisanship in Washington.http://www.cnn.com/2017/11/27/opinions/reps-bipartisanship-in-washington-is-happening-opinion-reed-gottheimer/index.html …
